title: Grocery Shopping
text: Buy milk, eggs, bread, fruits and vegetables from the supermarket.

title: Car Maintenance
text: Take the car to the mechanic for MOT.

title: Clean Garage
text: Clean out and organize the garage, dispose of any unnecessary items.

title: Laundry
text: Wash, dry and fold the laundry.

title: Pay Bills
text:
Pay the electricity, water, and internet bills for this month.
also need council tax!

title: Garden Work
text: Mow the lawn, water the plants, and remove any weeds from the garden.
